— Bernier,
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="128.[1975,2574,299,725]" lastBlockId="128.[1367,2574,732,1318]" pageId="128" pageNumber="729">Dorre, and Dirk Hartog Is, Shark Bay, Western Australia.</paragraph>
